Mrs. True has been married for six years.  She is employed full-time as an office administrator.  She stopped smoking January of this year, had a 20+ year of one-pack every two- to three-day history.  Alcohol use consists of one or two beverages per day.  She has two brothers alive and well.  On brother deceased from suicide.  She has one son and one daughter, ages 22 and 26.  Two grandchildren and three-step-grandchildren.  All of the children and grandchildren are in good health.

